Class FieldDefinitionImpl

java.lang.Object
com.commercetools.api.models.type.FieldDefinitionImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
FieldDefinition, ModelBase
public class FieldDefinitionImpl extends Object implements FieldDefinition, ModelBase

Defines a Custom Field and its meta-information. This FieldDefinition is similar to an AttributeDefinition of Product Types.
